## ðŸ§ª How It Works

1. User fills and submits the form.
2. Data is saved to the database.
3. Admin can click "Trigger" to launch the bot.
4. Laravel executes the Python script using `shell_exec`.
5. The Python bot (e.g., Selenium script) automates actions using the form data.